# Auto-assigns reviewers by matching changed files to the patterns below.
# Replace the @placeholders with real @usernames or @org/teams (they must have
# repo access). Two names on a line = both are requested.

# Default reviewers for everything.
*                   @your-tech-lead @your-project-owner

# Sensitive surfaces - Tech Lead reviews. Rename folders to match your project.
**/auth/**          @your-tech-lead
**/security/**      @your-tech-lead
**/migrations/**    @your-tech-lead
**/alembic/**       @your-tech-lead
/.github/**         @your-tech-lead

# Highest-risk areas - both Tech Lead and Project Owner.
**/billing/**       @your-tech-lead @your-project-owner
**/payments/**      @your-tech-lead @your-project-owner
